"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T13:17:26.000Z","msg":"Why 唔可以檢討？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T13:19:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不分化 不割席</span></span><br />\n<br />\n再檢討啫係鬥黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T13:33:02.000Z","msg":"檢討你做得唔好，叫咩鬥黃？<br />\n<br />\n「鬥黃」係指我捐一百你捐二百咁，你比我捐得多所以更黃，需要喺「同性質」嘅事物上作「比較」。做錯咪出嚟同選民跪地道歉兼改正，就係咁簡單，無人同你班友鬥。"},{"pid":"a34f03707794e62f8d9a0cd33751c493371c49ce","tid":1991513,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7a46cfcfa512c2df7372c80a5d1e6d7489f9bab","tid":1991513,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T12:54:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">我屌曬你地老母</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔講以為上緊熱狗Forum🌭🌭🌭</span><br />\n<br />\n成個熱門全部只係得批鬥梁耀忠葉建源post<br />\n全城中曬伏<br />\n視線成功被帶走<br />\n焦點去曬佢地果度<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">宜家家我地35+戰勝左喇咩？<br />\n係咪已經贏左？</span><br />\n<br />\n我地宜家要對付既係乜嘢？？？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>大家知唔知你興奮緊既時嘅敵方已經計劃緊DQ？</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請過左九點，停止再攻擊梁耀忠葉建源</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地宜家要對付既係乜嘢？？？<br />\n<br />\n我地必須沉着應戰<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">可唔可以梁耀忠葉建源當condom？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"h